@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
        <h1 class="card-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-10">
                <div class="alert alert-primary">
                    <div class="d-flex">
                        <div class="me-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt fa-2x text-primary"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="alert-heading">Your Privacy During Someren</h4>
                            <p class="mb-0">The Someren application processes personal data of students and lecturers participating in the annual Computer Science department study trip. This policy outlines how we handle this information.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3 class="mt-4 mb-3">Information Collection</h3>
                <p>The Someren application collects and processes the following types of data:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Student information (student number, first/last name, telephone number, class)</li>
                    <li>Lecturer information (first/last name, telephone number, age)</li>
                    <li>Room assignments in buildings A and B</li>
                    <li>Activity participation and supervision records</li>
                    <li>Bar transactions (vouchers and drink consumption)</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="mt-4 mb-3">How We Use Your Data</h3>
                <p>Your data is used exclusively for:</p>
                <div class="row mt-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-light text-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-users text-primary mb-3" style="font-size: 2rem;"></i>
                            <h5>Trip Management</h5>
                            <p class="small mb-0">Organizing accommodations and activities</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-light text-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-bed text-primary mb-3" style="font-size: 2rem;"></i>
                            <h5>Room Assignment</h5>
                            <p class="small mb-0">Managing dormitory and room allocations</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-light text-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-cash-register text-primary mb-3" style="font-size: 2rem;"></i>
                            <h5>Bar Operations</h5>
                            <p class="small mb-0">Tracking drink vouchers and inventory</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3 class="mt-4 mb-3">Voucher and Bar Data</h3>
                <p>For legal and tax purposes, we track drink consumption at the Monday evening Disco. This includes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Types of drinks purchased (alcoholic and non-alcoholic)</li>
                    <li>VAT calculations (9% for non-alcoholic, 21% for alcoholic)</li>
                    <li>Voucher redemption records</li>
                    <li>Bar duty assignments for lecturers</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="mt-4 mb-3">Data Retention</h3>
                <p>Personal information is retained only for the duration necessary to organize and manage the Someren trip. Activity and bar records may be kept longer for accounting and tax purposes as required by law.</p>

                <h3 class="mt-4 mb-3">Data Security</h3>
                <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect all personal information regarding students, lecturers, accommodations, activities, and bar operations.</p>

                <h3 class="mt-4 mb-3">Department Access</h3>
                <p>This information is accessible only to authorized Computer Science department staff responsible for organizing and managing the Someren trip.</p>

                <div class="alert alert-light border mt-5">
                    <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Last updated: March 2025. This privacy policy applies specifically to the Someren application and related activities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>